    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0

    v2 = wp.exp(wp.cos(wp.sin(v2 + 0.72)))
    v2 = (tmp / (v1 + (v2 + 0.31 - v0 + 0.53)))
    v2 = v2
    tmp = wp.cos(((v0 + 0.01 + v2 + 0.59) * (v0 + 0.27 / v1 + 0.61)))
    tmp = (0.65 * wp.sin(v2))
    v2 = tmp
    v1 = wp.cos(((tmp + 0.80 - v1 + 0.43) - wp.abs(tmp + 0.17)))
    data[tid] = v0
